Run a vprof of an executable.

#### Examples

    [lang=csharp]
    var profilingResults = Profiler.Profile(
        @"D:\dev\MyApp\MyApp.exe",
        "",
        @"D:\dev\MyApp",
        true);
    foreach (var profilingResult in profilingResults)
    {
        profilingResult.Dump();
        Console.WriteLine("==================================\n");
    }
